  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1480440/extras/fdcbd1a859951a858320e35a119d44cb.webp?t=1667016870\" width=300 height=52 /></span><br>★This is a desktop nurturing kitten pet that can be placed anywhere on your computer desktop.<br>★You can customize your pet's name and give her a nice name.<br>★She needs you to take good care of her food life. According to your training, she will become better and better or she may die.<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1480440/extras/6d342a4310940c44f30752ee564a5c24.webp?t=1667016870\" width=300 height=52 /></span><br>★Take good care of your pet, she also has emotions. You also need to eat and bathe.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1480440/extras/f72c30da92392738bde04cf45b8096e4.poster.avif?t=1667016870\" width=382 height=560 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1480440/extras/f72c30da92392738bde04cf45b8096e4.webm?t=1667016870\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1480440/extras/f72c30da92392738bde04cf45b8096e4.mp4?t=1667016870\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1480440/extras/e1f081e729f0d03d7f737ee2b5dac40b.webp?t=1667016870\" width=300 height=52 /></span><br>★Have 20 + hairstyles and clothes in the game, try to make your pet change into a new one.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1480440/extras/e55ede63efae2